ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectUnited Nations Multidimensional Integrated Stabilization Mission in Mali (MINUSMA) Medal Order
PrecisOrder (a) authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the United Nations Multidimensional Integrated Stabilization Mission in MALI (MINUSMA) Medal in recognition of honourable service; and (b) directing that the Medal follow the United Nations Mission in the REPUBLIC OF SOUTH SUDAN (UNMISS) Medal in the order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
